  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb3 \u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Menace by underworld gangs \u2013 protection for police",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Information has been revealed that many policemen who directly participated in drug roundup and control activities of the underworld have received threats to their lives through the underworld group.",
        "It is learned that many witnesses of drug cases in the country and members of the drug network have been killed by unidentified gunmen and that the Intelligence Department has reported this information to the Inspector General of Police.",
        "Accordingly, it is known that special protection has been given to many policemen, including two chief police inspectors who have now retired from police service. Police sources said that among those who have been secured, a senior police inspector in charge of a zone in the Western Province is included.",
        "Also, it is known that the police chief has advised the police who are facing this threat to pay more attention to their personal safety."
      ],
